per cent to Dollars 163.7m on revenues that were 4 per cent better at
Dollars 775.9m.
In the filmed entertainment division, operating income jumped by 84 per cent
to Dollars 156.7m on revenues that were 45 per cent higher at Dollars
929.8m.
Operating income in the consumer products business was 18 per cent up at
Dollars 86.2m on revenues that were 34 per cent higher at Dollars 320.7m.
