Trading                     9.9   11.3   12.3   13.2   16.2   16.3
Investment Banking          5.2    5.2    4.1    3.2    6.1    7.5
Mutual Funds                2.2    1.4    1.6    1.7    2.1    2.8
Fees                        1.8    1.9    2.2    2.2    2.5    3.1
Other*                     19.0   23.2   29.1   24.8   23.8   21.5
